screen_desc: This is the Google Play Store page for the Lyft app. It shows the app's name, rating (3.9 stars from 296K reviews), download count (50M+), and a description of the app's features like safety and cost transparency. Below the app screenshots, it also includes an "Install" button for downloading the app. Additionally, there's a section about the app’s data safety practices.
history_actions: click on the "Play Store" icon located at the right and lower part of the screen.
click on the magnifying glass search icon located at the top-right corner.
click on the search bar located at the top right.
type in the content: "Lyft - Rideshare, Bikes, Scooters & Transit"
click on the Lyft app icon located at the top-left.
action_plan: Tap the 'Install' button to bring up the options menu and look for the 'Uninstall' option.
